title: xNovel Collection 2008-12-27
description:
Contains 1,299 adult novels from defunct publishers such as Greenleaf Classics, Liverpool Library, Beeline Novels and Heatherpool Press.

Each zip archive contains a novel in text format and in most cases, a scan of the cover in jpeg format. Also included is a listing of titles in tab-delimited text format.

This torrent is a convenient solution for those wanting to download the entire collection at the xNovel site.

For more information, or to read the novels online for free, visit http://neatopotato.net/xnovel/.
